  <brief_title>Laser Acupuncture Against Nausea in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laser Acupuncture to Alleviate Nausea and Vomiting in Children and Adolescents Receiving Highly Emetogenic Chemotherapy. A Prospective, Double-Blinded, Placebo-Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
